WEBVTT

00:00:00.724 --> 00:00:02.523
Women represent

00:00:02.523 --> 00:00:05.574
50 percent of middle management

00:00:05.574 --> 00:00:08.363
and professional positions,

00:00:08.363 --> 00:00:11.491
but the percentages of women
at the top of organizations

00:00:11.491 --> 00:00:14.315
represent not even a third of that number.

00:00:14.315 --> 00:00:17.820
So some people hear that statistic and they ask,

00:00:17.820 --> 00:00:21.323
why do we have so few women leaders?

00:00:21.323 --> 00:00:23.246
